cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.GR, cs.AI 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with facial image beautification and makeup synthesis. It could also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves image processing and synthesis. Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) is another likely sub-category as the system is designed for common users. Graphics (cs.GR) is also a possibility as it involves the synthesis of makeup attributes onto facial images. Finally, Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) could be a potential sub-category as the makeup recommendation model involves learning and predicting the most suitable makeup attributes.
